reviewText: Great dvd!  Very funny, he sings, dances, jokes!  I can see why he calls himself the entertainer!  Would definitely recommend it and wish he had a more current dvd.
Title: Cedric the Entertainer - Taking You Higher

Title: Cedric the Entertainer - Taking You Higher

reviewText: My boyfriend and i LOVE to watch standups...and Cedric is one of the best.  If you like Cedric, you'll like this one.  Very entertaining!
Title: Cedric the Entertainer - Taking You Higher

reviewText: Cedric made a good comeback with this stand up routine. I mean this show is absolutely hilarious. Sort of reminds me of when he was on  def comedy jam. A wide variety of topics are discussed and made fun of in this show. Full of classic material from beginning to end. One of my favorites is Jerry rice on Dancing with the stars. A great addition to your dvd collection.
Title: Cedric the Entertainer - Taking You Higher
